This is how to encode of message:
  Remember that result is []
  Do this message's length times:
    Remember that i is diff of result's length and 0
    Remember that ch is item i in message
    When ch is in "aeiouAEIOU", then:
      Add result to ch
    End when
    When ch is more than 96, then:
      Remember that code is diff of ch and 32
      When code is 69, then:
        Remember that code is 71
      End when
      When code is 73, then:
        Remember that code is 75
      End when
      When code is 79, then:
        Remember that code is 81
