    When ch is less than 65, then:
      Add result to ch
    End when
    When ch is more than 90, then:
      When ch is at least 96, then:
        Add result to ch
      End when
    End when
  End do
  When isstring of message, then:
    Remember that text is ""
    Do this result's length times:
      Remember that i is diff of text's length and 0
      Remember that text is "{text}{item i in result}"
    End do
